Game da yanayin garin, yana kusa da bakin teku, wanda zai iya taimakawa wajen kara yawan lalacewar bala'in.
Nugraho ya bayyana lamarin a matsayin "babban bala'i" kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, cibiyoyin kasuwanci da otal-otal sun lalace.
An gano gawarwakin wadanda suka mutu a cikin rushewar gine-ginen, ya kara da cewa mutane 540 sun ji rauni a hatsarin, kuma ana neman mutane 29.
Nughroho ya kuma ce yiwuwar mutuwar mutane da lalacewar ta fi girma a arewacin Palau, mai nisan kilomita 300 (190 miles) daga garin, a yankin Donggala, inda ake da cibiyar girgizar kasar.
Sadarwa "ta kasance iyakance sosai dangane da isar da bayanai" tsakanin Dongola da sauran masu ruwa da tsaki, in ji Nugroho.
