Trump yana jawabi a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara yakin neman zabe a yau a Willing, West Virginia.
Wannan shine farkon taron Trump na biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, sannan kuma wurare kamar Tennessee da Mississippi suna cikin jerin wuraren da za a je.
A cikin wata takarda da kotun kolin ta aika, ta bayyana cewa, Trump zai samu goyon baya a zaben da ake yi a watan Nuwamba, saboda akwai barazanar cewa 'yan Republican za su rasa iko a majalisar dokokin kasar.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia kuma ta yaya za mu iya kallon sa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump na yammacin Virginia a karfe 7 na safe yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
