Daliban Harvard sun ɗauki darasi game da samun isashen hutu.
Jami'ar Harvard ta buɗe wani kwas na musamman ga dukan ɗalibai da ke mai da hankali kan koya wa ɗalibai su sami isasshen hutu, yayin da matasa suke yawan shan ƙwayoyi masu saurin ƙonewa da kuma shan maganin kafeyin.
Masana kimiyya sun gano cewa ɗaliban da suka je jami'a mafi girma ba su san yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Zisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya kirkiro wannan darasi, wanda ya ce shi ne na farko a Amurka.
Ya fara wannan darasin ne bayan ya fahimci yadda rashin barci yake shafar koyo.
'Wata yarinya ta zo wurina bayan na halarci taro kuma ta ce, 'Me ya sa kuke gaya mini wannan a wannan lokacin, a lokacin da nake babban shekara?'
Ya ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya masa game da bukatar barci, abin mamaki,' in ji ta.
An soma wannan darasin ne a shekara ta farko, kuma babban manufarsa shi ne a koya wa ɗalibai yadda samun isashen barci zai iya shafan karatunsu da kuma ƙwarewarsu a wasanni da kuma lafiyarsu.
Paul Barrera, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma shugaban jami'ar kiwon lafiya ta Harvard, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da irin wannan karatun ne bayan ta lura da yawan yaran da ke fama da matsalar bacci a cikin mako guda.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da ayyuka masu ma'amala.
Wani sashen hoton da aka nuna yana nuna abubuwa kamar kofuna na kofi, labule, takalman motsa jiki da kuma littattafai, kuma ya bayyana yadda maganin kafeyin da hasken rana ke shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma yadda yin barci yake da muhimmanci.
A wani ɓangaren kuma, ana tambayar masu sauraro game da haɗarin shan wahala daga ciwon zuciya, ciwon daji, da kuma baƙin ciki idan ba su yi barci sosai ba.
Taswirar da ke cikin harabar makarantar, tare da alamun da ke ciki, yana sa ɗalibai su yi tunani game da al'adarsu ta yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa waɗannan abubuwan ba za su canja halayen ɗalibanmu nan take ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da hakkin su sani - kamar yadda suke da hakkin sanin sakamakon shan taba,' in ji Farfesa Zidler.
Al'adar 'yin barci da dare' ta ci gaba, in ji shi, ya daɗa cewa fasahar zamani da matsin lamba a kan ɗalibai suna ƙara ƙaruwa ga matsalar rashin barci.
Da kyau, samun isashen barci ya kamata ya zama 'makaminmu na sirri' don magance damuwa, gajiya, da haushi - kuma don guje wa kiba, domin rashin barci yana sa jikinmu ya ji yunwa kuma yana sa su ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond Shaw, ɗan shekara 19 daga California, wanda ke nazarin ilmin sunadarai da ilimin halittu na zahiri, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Sizzler ya tsara darasin bayan Shaw ya yi masa aji ɗaya da Farfesa a shekarar da ta gabata a matsayin ɗan shekara ɗaya.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya motsa shi ya ɗauki darasi mai ma'ana.
Mataki na gaba da yake fata shi ne, ya bukaci duk wani da ya kammala karatun ya dauki irin wannan darasi kafin ya koma makarantar.
Farfesa Zidler ya shawarci dalibai su saita ƙararrawa kafin su kwanta da kuma kafin su tashi, kuma ya ce ɗalibai su guji "hasken shuɗi" da allon lantarki da hasken LED ke nunawa, wanda zai iya canza saurin bugun zuciya sosai, wanda zai haifar da rikicewar bacci.
Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Goal na Manga ya doke yaran Gerard
Rangers sun sake shan kaye a gida bayan da Dolly Minga ta doke Steven Gerrard da ci 1-0.
Ita dai kungiyar ta Ibrox ta nemi nasarar farko bayan da ta doke St Johnstone da ci 4-1 a watan Fabrairun da ya gabata, amma kungiyar ta Gary Holt ta doke Gerrard, ta kuma kai shi ga rashin nasara a wasanni 18 a matsayin manajan, inda ta bar tawagar ta tazarar da Ledbrook da maki takwas a ragar shugabannin gasar Premier.
Minga ta buga kwallo da minti bakwai kafin karshen rabin farko, ta karya layin Rangers wanda ya kasance a cikin kiran da ba a kira ba.
Yayin da Rangers ta koma ta shida, Livingston ta koma ta uku, ta ci Hibernian da ci daya.
Kuma a wani bangare kuma, Rangers na iya fuskantar wata matsala bayan da Calum Spencer, dan wasan kungiyar, ya ji rauni a kai sakamakon harbin bindiga.
Gerard ya yi canje-canje takwas a wasan a cikin tawagar da ta doke Ayr a wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin duniya.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya ci gaba da buga wasanni 11 da ya ci a makon da ya gabata, kuma yana godiya ga yadda 'yan wasansa ke amsawa a kowane wasa.
Rangers na iya samun karin kwallon amma Livingston ya fi su.
A ka'ida, Rangers ya kamata a buga shi minti biyu kafin Menga ya iya samun kwallon Scott Pittman a raga na farko, amma Rangers ya ci gaba da kai hari, wanda ya ci gaba da tseren.
Dan wasan kwallon kafa Keegan Jacobs ya buga kwallo a raga, sai dai dan wasan baya Alan Lithgow ya samu nasarar sake buga kwallo.
Rangers sun sake samun kwallon, amma a ƙarshe sun nuna ba da bege ba amma da imani.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi imanin cewa za a ba shi damar buga kwallo bayan da ya buga Steven Lawless, amma alkalin wasa ya soke bukatar ta ta hanyar tashi da tutar.
Rangers sun yi kokari wajen buga kwallo biyu a farkon rabin wasan, amma Liam Kelly, mai tsaron gidan abokan hamayyarsa, bai yi matukar wahalar cin kwallo biyu da Lasana da Ovie Ejaria suka yi ba.
A wannan lokacin, bugun da Livingston ya yi a minti na 34 zai iya zama mai yanke hukunci, kuma babu wanda zai iya musun cewa ya yi hakan.
Har ila yau, Rangers ba su iya yin tsayayya da tsaron da Jacobs ya yi ba.
Scott Arfield bai yi wani abu ba saboda Declan Gallagher ya ba da kwallon ga Robinson wanda ya yi nasara kuma ya ba da Mango don kawo karshen harin.
Gerard ya maye gurbin Ryan Kent a hutu kuma ya yi tasiri a gefen, amma wani abu da ya faru a cikin tsaro ya rushe shi.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da tafiya cikin sauri kuma ya kashe abokan hamayyarsa ta hanyar amfani da dogon lokaci na Lithgow da Hacklet.
Holt zai iya samun nasara a karshe, amma McGregor ya tsaya a filin wasa kuma bai ba da damar kowane motsawar da Jacobs ya yi ba har sai Lithgow ya kira daga nesa.
A lokacin da Rangers suka yi canji, Glenn Middleton ya nemi a ba shi bugun daga baya, amma alkalin ya ki amincewa da hakan.
