Kuma yanzu shafi na wannan makon: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka gabata, kuma har yanzu muna cikin lissafi... ranar da aka haifi mai ilimin lissafi na gaba Johann Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Gaiger ya kirkiro wata hanyar da za ta iya lissafawa da kuma gano radiyo, wani abu da ya kafa tushen binciken Gaiger.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, a cikin kimiyya, giya ta Geiger ta zama wani ɓangare na al'adun gargajiya, har ma a cikin fim na 1950 "A cikin Colorado Bell" wanda ke nuna mai binciken Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Wane irin duniya ce wannan?"
Rogers: Wannan shi ne Geiger's hammer, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen sarrafa ma'adanai masu saurin gudu kamar uranium.
Idan ka sa wadannan belun kunne, zaka iya jin tasirin sinadarin da ke cikin atomatik wanda ke haifar da radiation".
Evans: "Ka ce, yana da gaske a wannan lokacin!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kaɗan kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
