Tauraron "Game of Thrones", Keith Harrington ya yi magana game da "mutumin mai guba"
Keith Harrington sananne ne saboda rawar da John Snow ya taka a cikin HBO fantasy series Game of Thrones.
Aikin da aka yi wa 'yar fim mai shekaru 31 ya nuna cewa, idan aka ga maza suna yin irin wannan aikin, sai su yi tunanin cewa idan sun yi hakan, za su sami daraja daga mutane.
A wata hira da The Sunday Times Culture, Keith ya ce "wani abu ba daidai ba ne" kuma yana sha'awar yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa a cikin #MeToo.
Kitty, wadda ta yi aure kwanan nan da Rose Leslie, 'yar fim mai suna "Game of Thrones", mai shekara 31, ta ce tana da ƙarfin hali wajen jimre wa wannan matsalar.
"Yanzu na tabbata cewa, 'A ina muka yi kuskure game da namiji?'
"Me muka koya wa yara maza lokacin da suke girma? Wannan shine dalilin da yasa muke ganin wadannan matsalolin yanzu".
Keith ya yi imanin cewa akwai wani ɓangare na wannan matsala da ke haifar da nuna jaruntaka a talabijin.
Ya ci gaba da cewa, "Menene dabi'a, kuma menene darussa?
Shin abin da ake koyarwa a kan titi da talabijin yana sa yara maza su ɗauki matakin da ake kira kasancewa maza?
Ina tsammanin daya daga cikin muhimman tambayoyin zamaninmu shine, ta yaya zamu canza wannan?
Domin babu shakka, akwai wani abu da bai dace da samari ba".
A wata hira da aka yi da shi, ya yarda cewa ba zai taɓa yin wasa da "Game of Thrones" ba lokacin da aka buga jerin karshe a bazara mai zuwa. Ya ce "ya rage filin wasa da dawakai".
A watan Nuwamba, Kitty za ta fito a fim din Sam Shepard na True West, wanda ke ba da labarin wani mai shirya fim da kuma ɗan'uwansa da ya yi fashi.
Actor din ya ce mafi kyawun abin da ya faru a "Game da Gidan Gida" shi ne ya sadu da matarsa, Rose.
"Na sadu da matata a wannan wasan kwaikwayon, kuma a gaskiya, wannan wasan kwaikwayon ya sa na sami iyali. Wannan shi ne inda rayuwata ta fara", in ji shi.
Rose ta taka rawar Ighritty, wanda ke son halin Keith, Jon Snow a cikin jerin almara na Emmy.
Ma'aurata sun yi aure a watan Yuni na 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
AIDS: China ta yi rahoton karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin 100
China ta sanar da cewa adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar kanjamau ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Mutane sama da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an ma'aikatar lafiya.
Kimanin sabbin mutane 40,000 ne aka samu a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018.
Yawancin su an ba su ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da abubuwan da suka gabata.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a sassa daban-daban na kasar Sin ta hanyar jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ya kusan zuwa sifili, in ji jami'an ma'aikatar lafiya ta kasar Sin a wani taro da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, adadin mutanen da ke fama da cutar kanjamau a ƙasar Sin yana ƙaruwa da 100,000 kowace shekara.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT a China.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna wa LGBTI nuna bambanci.
Bincike ya nuna cewa domin al'adar kasar, kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin dari na maza da suke kwana da maza za su yi aure.
Ana iya kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar yin jima'i ta hanyar rashin amfani da kariya.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da magani ga kowa don magance cutar.
