A wannan Lahadi, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin 'yan kasa na duniya, wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke da manyan taurari masu rawar gani da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa don kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
A yanzu, a shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Citizen na Duniya zai ga dubban mutane suna taruwa a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park don ba kawai su ji daɗin jawabin Janet Jackson da Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron, wanda shine kawo ƙarshen talauci ta 2030.
Bikin Baƙi na Duniya, wanda aka fara a 2012, wani ci gaba ne na aikin talauci na duniya, ƙungiyar talla ta duniya, wanda ke fatan kawo ƙarshen talauci ta hanyar haɓaka yawan mutanen da ke yaƙi da shi.
Don samun tikiti kyauta zuwa taron (sai dai idan kuna son siyan tikiti na VIP), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayon dole ne su cika wasu ayyuka, ko "ayyukan" kamar yin aikin sa kai, rubuta wa shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya, ko kuma a kowace hanya mai mahimmanci don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin dalilin taron, wanda shine kawo ƙarshen talauci.
Amma, shin yaya nasarar bikin na 'yan ƙasa a duniya, shekaru 12 kafin a cimma burin?
Shin kyautar kyauta kyauta ce hanya madaidaiciya ta lallashe mutane suyi aiki, ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "collectivism" - lokacin da mutane suke tunanin cewa suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda kai ta yanar gizo, ko kuma aikawa a shafin Twitter?
Tun daga 2011, Citizen Duniya ya gaya mana cewa ya sami sama da "aiki" miliyan 19 daga magoya bayansa, yana tura masu masaukin baki zuwa manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce, wannan aiki ya taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su yi alkawari da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayukan mutane biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta yi tsokaci kan alkawura da sanarwa 390 da suka samo asali daga ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka rarraba ko aka tara.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa an riga an yi amfani da kudaden da aka bayar kai tsaye ga mutane sama da miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin waɗannan alkawuran shine ƙarfin abinci, haɗin gwiwar masu saka hannun jari da masu fasaha na Burtaniya sun yi alƙawarin "taimaka wa yara su cika damar su", alƙawarin ba da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa wajen kawo ƙarshen karancin abinci a ƙasar bayan karɓar saƙonni sama da 4,700 daga 'yan ƙasa a duniya.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa da 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci a tarihi", in ji jakadan Food Force, Tracey Ullman ga masu sauraro a wani wasan kwaikwayo na raye a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan gudanar da ayyuka sama da 5,000 da ke kira ga Burtaniya da ta inganta abinci ga mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za ta ba da tallafi ga wani shiri, Food Force, wanda zai isa ga mata da yara miliyan 5 ta hanyar samar da abinci.
