Amurka na iya amfani da sojan ruwanta wajen "kulle" Rasha don hana fitar da makamashi - ministan cikin gida
"Idan ya cancanta", Washington na iya amfani da sojojin ruwanta don hana makamashi na Rasha, da kuma shiga kasuwa, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi jayayya cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Syria - musamman ma inda take aiki a gayyatar gwamnati ta halal - dalili ne na bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Na yi imani dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne don su yi kasuwanci da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, a kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma bisa ga bayanan hukuma, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin da za a magance shi.
"Amurka tana da ikon, ta hanyar sojan ruwanmu, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa sun bude kuma idan ya cancanta, don toshewa don tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba zai shiga kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar masu amfani da makamashi ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta wacce ke kiran kanta "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya tafi ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke tunkarar Rasha da Iran, ya ce sun yi kama da juna.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki game da Rasha da Iran, aƙalla, shine amfani da makamashi a matsayin burka da maye gurbin", in ji shi, yana mai ambaton Rasha a matsayin "mai ƙwarewa ɗaya" wanda tattalin arzikinta ya dogara da burbushin mai.
Rahotanni sun ce gwamnatin Trump na da burin kara fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai da kuma maye gurbin Rasha, wani zaɓi mai rahusa ga masu amfani da Turai.
Don haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta ki amincewa da aikin bututun mai mai mai "Nord Stream 2", wanda Trump ya ce ya sa Berlin ta zama "ƙugiya" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta jaddada cewa aikin famfo mai daraja dala biliyan 11 na Nord Stream 2, wanda aka tsara don ninka girman bututun mai zuwa mita biliyan 110 na murabba'in, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya ce rashin amincewar da Washington ke yi da aikin na da nasaba da tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Na yi imanin cewa mun yarda cewa ba za a iya amfani da makamashi a matsayin hanyar matsa lamba ba kuma cewa masu amfani su sami damar zaɓar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Alexander Novak, bayan ganawa da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Matsayin Amurka ya haifar da rashin jin daɗi daga Jamus, wanda ya tabbatar da kasancewarsa cikin aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta yi watsi da manufofin samar da makamashi na Tarayyar Turai da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata ƙasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi", in ji shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI), Dieter Kempf, bayan ganawar da aka yi tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren "za ta yi la'akari da gaske" game da neman takarar shugaban kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Laraba za ta "daure ido sosai" ta nemi takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben fidda gwani.
A cikin garin Holloway, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa yana tunanin shiga.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya hada da samun mace a cikin shugabanci", in ji ta, a cewar Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da gaske game da neman shugaban kasa".
Warren ya kira shugaban kasa Donald Trump a lokacin da yake cikin gari, ya ce ya "kai wannan kasa cikin hanyar da ba daidai ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke lalata wa dimokiradiyya", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai gaskiya a cikin sukarsa ga Trump da dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa, "Tabbas muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin a kada kuri'a".
Amma, wani binciken da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'ar Warren ba su yi imanin cewa ya kamata ya yi zabe a shekarar 2020 ba.
A cewar wani binciken da Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk da Boston Globe suka yi, kashi 88 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata Sanatan ya kada kuri'a ba.
Kashi 32 cikin dari na goyon bayan wannan takarar.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya ga tsohon gwamna Deval Patrick, inda kashi 38 cikin dari ke goyon bayan dan takarar da kashi 48 cikin dari ke adawa da shi.
Wasu sanannun sunaye a cikin 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat suna la'akari da yiwuwar zaben 2020 na Mataimakin Shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a watan Janairu, in ji Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta yi tsokaci game da matsalar damuwa ta PTSD na Trump
Trac Palin, mai shekara 26, ya yi shekara guda a Iraki bayan da aka tura shi aiki a watan Satumba.
An kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da aikata wani mummunan aiki a cikin gida a ranar Litinin da dare.
"Abin da ɗana yake fuskanta, abin da ya fuskanta lokacin da ya dawo, na danganta shi ga sauran iyalai da ke fama da ciwon damuwa da raunin da sojojinmu suka dawo da shi", in ji ta ga masu sauraro a wani taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira kama ta "rufe ido ga wata matsala ta fili" kuma ta ce game da ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji, "Suna dawowa da ɗan canji, suna dawowa da baƙin ciki, suna dawowa da mamaki idan suna samun girmamawa kamar yadda abokansu sojoji da matukan jirgi da sauran sojoji suka ba da kansu ga ƙasarsu".
An kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mace a gida, Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun ofishin 'yan sanda na Wasilla ya ce, "Ya yi ikirarin aikata laifin cin zarafin mata a gida da kuma dauke da makami a lokacin da ba shi da hankali".
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan sabuwar dokar neman mafaka
Jihohi goma sha shida da gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan kalubalen shari'a game da sabuwar manufar Amurka da ba ta ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke fama da tashin hankali ko tashin hankali na gida.
A ranar Juma'a, a Washington, D.C., wakilan jihohi 18 da na gundumar Columbia sun gabatar da wata takarda mai kama da ta kotu don tallafawa masu neman mafaka, wanda ke haifar da siyasa, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara ba a cikin shari'ar Grace Sessions da Civil Liberties Union ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta game da manufofin tarayya.
Ya ce abokin aikinsa "da 'ya'yansa' yan kungiyar ta'addanci sun cin zarafinsa, amma jami'an Amurka sun hana shi neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An kama shi a Texas.
Jami'an gwamnati da ke goyon bayan Grace sun ambaci El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, waɗanda ke samar da manyan masu neman mafaka a Amurka saboda waɗannan ƙasashe suna fuskantar manyan matsalolin ƙungiyoyi da tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke hukuncin da Kotun Kula da Shige da Fice ta yanke a shekarar 2014 wanda ya baiwa bakin haure damar tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida da neman mafaka.
Babban mai kula da yankin Columbia, Carl Racine, ya bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na jihar, tarayya da kuma dokokin kasa da kasa".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci duk wani bukatar neman mafaka ya dogara ne da takamaiman hujjoji da yanayin da ake nema, kuma wannan ƙuntatawa ya sabawa wannan ƙa'idar", in ji mai shari'a.
Masu sauraro sun yi jayayya a kan taƙaitaccen bayanin cewa manufofin da ke hana baƙi shiga suna lalata manufofin Amurka, suna cewa za su sa su zama masu ƙwarewa kuma "su samar mana da ma'aikata da muke buƙata".
Babban mai kula da shi Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice a watan Yuni da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke fama da tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma ƙungiyoyi.
"Sai dai, an ba da mafaka ga wadanda suka bar kasarsu saboda tsananin ko tsoron tsanantawa saboda launin fata, addini, kasa, ko kuma kasancewarsu a wata kungiya ko kuma ra'ayin siyasa", in ji Sessions a ranar 11 ga Yuni, lokacin da yake sanar da manufar.
Babu mafaka da za ta iya magance dukan matsalolin da mutane ke fuskanta a kowace rana a faɗin duniya.
