Tom Daley ya ji kamar yana da matsala game da jima'i
Mai wasan ƙwallon ƙafa na Olympics, Tom Dale ya ce ya girma yana jin ƙyamar wasu saboda ra'ayinsa na jima'i - amma hakan ya motsa shi ya yi nasara.
Ta ce ba ta san hakan ba sai da ta je makarantar sakandare, inda "ba kowa ba ne kamar ni".
A karo na farko, a wani jawabi da ya yi a gidan rediyo na Desert Island Discs, wanda Lauren Laverne ke jagoranta, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin maza don ya ba wasu "bege".
Ta kuma bayyana cewa tun lokacin da ta zama mahaifiyarta, ba ta da sha'awar lashe gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da wasan kwaikwayon mai tsawo, Kirsty Young, ya yi aiki na watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
Bayan da aka nuna ta a cikin shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya bayyana cewa yayin da yake girma, ya ji "ƙananan" ga wasu saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba idan ya kasance da sha'awar yara maza da mata".
Ya ce, "A yau, jin cewa na fi wasu da kuma bambanci gaskiya ne, kuma hakan ya ba ni ƙarfin yin nasara".
Tana so ta nuna cewa ita "wani abu ne", in ji ta, don kada ta ba kowa kunya idan sun san halin da take ciki.
Wannan mai lambar tagulla ta Olympics sau biyu ya zama sanannen mai fafutukar LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da kamanninsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don ƙara yawan ƙasashe don yin zanga-zanga game da nuna bambanci tsakanin luwadi.
Ta ce ta yi muryarta ne domin ta yi sa'ar rayuwa ba tare da nuna bambanci ba kuma tana son ta ba wasu "bege".
Ta ce ta yi soyayya da wani mutum - mai shirya fina-finai na Amurka Dustin Lance Blake, wanda ta sadu da shi a 2013 - "Ya kama ni ba zato ba tsammani".
Dale ta auri Oscar, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, a shekarar da ta gabata, amma ta ce bambancin shekaru bai taɓa zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da na samu wannan a shekarunka" - ya shiga gasar Olympics ta farko yana da shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani a shekarunsa wanda ya sami irin wannan tashe-tashen hankula da rashin sa'a.
Ma'auratan sun haifi ɗa a watan Yuni, wanda suka sa wa suna Robert Ray Black-Dale, kuma Dale ya ce "tsarin darajarsa" ya canza.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da na ke so shi ne na lashe zinare", in ji shi.
"Kun san, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
"Na samu lambar zinariya a cikin wannan wasa".
An sa wa ɗanta suna bayan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana ɗan shekara 40 bayan an gano cewa yana da ciwon daji a kwakwalwa.
Daley ta ce mahaifinta bai yarda da cewa ya mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin tambayoyin da ta yi a baya shi ne ko suna da tikiti zuwa London 2012 - domin tana son zama a gaban layin.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba, 'Ba za ka iya zama a kan gaba ba, Baba,'" in ji ta.
"Na riƙe hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi, kuma ba har sai da ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu ba, ban gane cewa ba shi da mutuwa ba", in ji ta.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daly ta yi tsere a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ta lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da na yi mafarkin rayuwata duka - in yi wasa a gaban magoya baya a gasar Olympics, babu abin da ya fi wannan", in ji ta.
Wannan kuma ya sa ta fara rubuta waƙar ta ta farko, Proud by Heather Small, wadda ta yi ta murna a gasar Olympics kuma har yanzu tana rera waka.
Za a watsa shirin Desert Island Discs a gidan rediyon BBC Radio 4 ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 na dare.
A ranar Laraba ne aka yi wa Michelson takarar gasar Ryder Cup.
Phil Michelson na Amurka zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi lokacin da ya buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47, amma dole ne ya dawo cikin tsari kafin ya zama abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda zai shiga gasar a karo na 12 a cikin shekaru biyu, ya shiga cikin wasannin da kyaftin Jim Furyk ya yi a ranar Lahadi a wasan kwallon kafa da Forsam.
Maimakon zama a tsakiyar abin da ke faruwa, kamar yadda yake sau da yawa a Amurka, mai nasara sau biyar ya raba kwanakinsa tsakanin zama mai ba da farin ciki da kuma aiki a kan wasan da fatan zai gyara abin da ke damunsa.
Ba a taɓa samun direba mai ƙwarewa ba, ko da a lokacin da ya fi ƙwarewa, mai shekara 48 ba zai iya yin wasa a filin wasan golf na Le Golf National ba, wanda yake da tsawo da kuma tsawo don yin kuskure.
Kuma idan filin wasa bai isa ba, Michelson, a wasa na takwas na mako, zai fafata da zakaran Birtaniya mai suna Francesco Molinari, wanda ke fafatawa da Tom Fleetwood don lashe wasanni hudu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa suka fara wasa 12 a raga guda da maki hudu, a cikin wani yanayi mai zafi, wasan Michelson zai zama mai muhimmanci.
Furik ya nuna cewa yana da tabbaci ga mijinta, ba wai yana da abubuwa da yawa da zai faɗa masa ba.
"Mann ya fahimci rawar da nake takawa a yau, ya rungume ni, ya ba ni hannu, ya ce zai shirya gobe", in ji Furik.
"Yana da tabbaci sosai.
Yana cikin zauren masu daraja kuma ya karawa wadannan kungiyoyi da yawa a baya da kuma wannan makon.
Da alama ban san cewa zai buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi ƙoƙari na ƙara ƙayyadewa, amma wannan shi ne yadda ya yi aiki, kuma wannan ita ce hanyar da muka yi tunanin za mu bi.
Yana son ya kasance a wurin, kamar kowa".
A ranar Lahadi, Michelson zai doke Nick Faldo, wanda ya fi kowa buga gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan zai iya nuna ƙarshen aikin Ryder Cup wanda bai taɓa daidaitawa da manyan bayanansa ba.
Michelson ya ci 18, ya yi rashin nasara 20, kuma ya ci 7 da rabi, amma Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ya kawo wasu motsin zuciyar da ba a taɓa ji ba.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana son yin dariya game da mutane, kuma yana da kyakkyawan mutumin da ya kamata ku kasance a cikin tawagarku", in ji shi.
"Ina tsammanin matasa 'yan wasa sun shiga cikin shi, kamar yadda ya faru a wannan makon, wanda ya kasance mai kyau a gani.
Yana da fiye da wasa kawai".
Kyaftin Turai Thomas Bjorn ya san cewa babban bambanci zai iya ɓacewa nan ba da daɗewa ba
Thomas Bjorn, shugaban Turai, ya san cewa kasancewa a gaba a ranar karshe a gasar Ryder Cup zai iya zama tseren da ba shi da kyau.
Dan ya fara wasa a shekara ta 1997 a Valdemarama, inda Steve Ballesteros ya jagoranci tawagar da ta kasance da maki biyar a kan Amurkawa amma ta kusa zuwa ƙarshen layi ta hanyar da ta fi kusa, ta lashe 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Kuna tuna wa kanku cewa muna da babban bambanci a Walderama; muna da babban bambanci a Brooklyn inda muka rasa, da kuma a Walderama inda muka ci, amma kawai", in ji Bjorn, bayan sun yi nasara 5-3 a 2018 duka a ranar Juma'a da jiya lokacin da suka ci gaba da 10-6 a kan Le Golf National.
Don haka tarihi ya nuna min, da kuma kowa a cikin tawagar, cewa wannan ba ta ƙare ba.
Za ka yi wasa a kai a kai gobe.
Ka je ka yi abin da ya kamata.
Ba za a kammala ba har sai kun sami maki a kan allon.
Muna da manufa, kuma ita ce mu yi ƙoƙari mu lashe kofin, kuma wannan shi ne abin da muke mai da hankali a kai.
A wannan lokacin, ina cewa, "Ina kallon 'yan wasa 12 da ke gefenmu, amma mun san abin da ke gefenmu, manyan 'yan wasa a duniya".
Da yake farin ciki da yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi a wasan golf, Bjorn ya daɗa cewa: "Ban taɓa tunanin hakan ba.
Za mu sami wata dabba a gobe.
Za mu yi jawabai a kan kanmu gobe, kuma wannan abu ne daban.
Yana da kyau idan kana tsaye a can tare da abokin tarayya, lokacin da komai ke tafiya daidai, amma idan kana waje kadai, to kana zuwa ne a matsayin mai wasan golf.
Wannan shine sakon da ya kamata ku kai wa 'yan wasan ku, ku nuna mafi kyawunku gobe.
Yanzu, kana da abokin aikinka a baya, kuma dole ne ya fita kuma ya nuna mafi kyau. "
A bambanci da Bjorn, Jim Furyk a gefe guda yana tsammanin 'yan wasansa su yi aiki mafi kyau a matsayin mutum fiye da ma'aurata, tare da banda Jordan Spit da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka ɗauki maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Furyk da kansa ya kasance a bangarorin biyu na wannan babban hari na ranar da ta gabata, yana cikin ƙungiyar da ta ci nasara a Brooklyn kafin a ci shi a lokacin da Turai ta haifi "Miracle of the Medina".
"Na tuna da duk wani la'anar da aka yi a can", in ji shi lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda kyaftin Ben Crenshaw ya yi magana da 'yan wasansa a ranar karshe a 1999.
"Muna da manyan wasanni 12 gobe, amma kuna so ku fara da sauri kamar yadda kuka gani a Brooklyn, kamar yadda kuka gani a Madina.
Idan wannan motsi ya tafi hanya daya, yana sanya matsin lamba mai yawa a kan tsakiya.
Mun tsara mu kuma mun sanya 'yan wasanmu a waje kamar yadda muke ji, kamar yadda muka san, muna ƙoƙarin yin sihiri gobe. "
Thomas ya tsallake aikin don tsayayya da shi kuma ya sadu da Rory McElroy a cikin babban wasan, tare da Paul Casey, Justin Rose, John Rame, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Pulter tare da sauran 'yan Turai a saman rabin jere.
"Na fito da wannan jerin tare da wannan rukuni na mutane saboda ina tsammanin ya ƙunshi duk hanyar da ta wuce", in ji Björn lokacin da yake zaɓar waƙar.
Jamus ta sake jinkirta karbar sabon jirgin ruwan yaki
An shirya sabon jirgin ruwan don karbar jiragen ruwa na Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba za a iya karbarsa ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma hauhawar farashi, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An jinkirta karɓar Rheinland-Pfalz, sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin 2019, kamar yadda jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito wani jami'in soja.
An shirya jirgi don shiga cikin jirgi a 2014, amma matsalolin da suka biyo bayan bayarwa sun sa kammala wannan babban aikin ya zama da wahala.
Jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg guda hudu da rundunar jiragen ruwa ta umarci a 2007 ya zama maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
A bayyane yake cewa za su sami makamai masu linzami masu ƙarfi, da makamai masu linzami da na'urorin saukar da jirgi, da wasu fasahohin STEL, kamar rage radar, infrared da fasahar sauti.
Sauran muhimman siffofi sune tsawon lokaci - ya kamata a iya sanya sababbin jiragen ruwa daga tashar jiragen ruwa na gida har tsawon shekaru biyu.
Amma, jinkirin da ake yi a kai a kai yana nufin cewa sababbin jiragen ruwa na yaƙi - da aka yi niyyar ƙarfafa sojojin ruwa na Jamus - za su zama tsofaffi a lokacin da suka shiga aiki, in ji Die Zeit.
Jirgin ruwan F125 ya zama sanannen sanarwa a shekarar da ta gabata lokacin da rundunar sojan ruwan Jamus ta yi watsi da jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa kamfanin Blohm & Voss da ke Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojan ruwa ta Jamus ta mayar da jirgi ga mai gina jirgi bayan an kira shi.
Dalilin da ya sa aka janye shi ba a san shi ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu manyan "kurakurai na software da kayan aiki" wanda zai sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan an fara aikin yaƙi.
Kuskuren software ya kasance mai mahimmanci, saboda jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg yana aiki ne da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120 - kawai rabin ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na tsohuwar jirgin ruwa na Bremen.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyin nauyi, wanda ya rage yawan aikinsa kuma ya hana rundunar jiragen ruwa damar ingantawa a nan gaba.
Jirgin mai nauyin tan 7,000 zai ninka nauyin jirage iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Tare da kayan aiki mara kyau, farashin yana shafar aikin gaba ɗaya - haɗawa da sake shirya ma'aikatan - wani abu ne.
An ce ya kai Euro biliyan 3.1 (dala biliyan 3.6) - daga Euro biliyan 2.2.
Matsalar da ke tattare da sababbin jiragen ruwa na musamman yana da mahimmanci a yayin da aka yi gargadin cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa jirgin ruwan yana "tsere wa jiragen ruwa masu aiki".
Wani jami'in ya ce matsalar ta karu ne a tsawon lokaci, saboda tsofaffin jiragen ruwa sun daina aiki, amma ba a sake yin wasu ba.
Ya yi korafin cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai shiga cikin jirgin ruwa.
